HEADWORD: Noll
<hw>Noll</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>nol</ets>, AS.
<ets>hnoll</ets> top; akin to OHG. <ets>hnol</ets> top, head.]</ety>
<def>The head; the noodle.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
